    "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219410/extras/baff3c229f9c6b156950522be6dab89d.avif?t=1769932821\" width=600 height=145 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Los filósofos ya desperdician su tiempo y sus vidas pensando sobre el pensar.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >¿Por qué no divertirse mientras lo hacen?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219410/extras/00f43c1494f13571f404844137e5d17a.poster.avif?t=1769932821\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219410/extras/00f43c1494f13571f404844137e5d17a.webm?t=1769932821\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219410/extras/00f43c1494f13571f404844137e5d17a.mp4?t=1769932821\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Trolley Solution</strong> es una recopilación de minijuegos basada en el famoso dilema del tranvía, originalmente propuesto en 1967 por la filósofa británica Philippa Foot.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219410/extras/b1097ba16ab9c7cd45e8b344cd94187b.poster.avif?t=1769932821\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219410/extras/b1097ba16ab9c7cd45e8b344cd94187b.webm?t=1769932821\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219410/extras/b1097ba16ab9c7cd45e8b344cd94187b.mp4?t=1769932821\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Pon a prueba tu capacidad de pensamiento y elige entre la deontología y el utilitarismo en iteraciones humorísticas del problema. Desbloquea una variedad de minijuegos donde podrás poner a prueba tus habilidades de juego.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219410/extras/d8ccfb3daa059203ae9407fb68301719.poster.avif?t=1769932821\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219410/extras/d8ccfb3daa059203ae9407fb68301719.webm?t=1769932821\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219410/extras/d8ccfb3daa059203ae9407fb68301719.mp4?t=1769932821\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Desafíate a ti mismo y aprende conocimientos filosóficos importantes y útiles mientras expandes tu mente.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Características:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 20 variaciones del dilema del tranvía (más la original)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 20 minijuegos inspirados en cada variación</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Descargo de responsabilidad: Es posible que no aprendas nada útil o importante, ni expandas tu mente, al jugar este juego.</i></p>",
    "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219410/extras/baff3c229f9c6b156950522be6dab89d.avif?t=1769932821\" width=600 height=145 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Los filósofos ya desperdician su tiempo y sus vidas pensando sobre el pensar.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >¿Por qué no divertirse mientras lo hacen?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219410/extras/00f43c1494f13571f404844137e5d17a.poster.avif?t=1769932821\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219410/extras/00f43c1494f13571f404844137e5d17a.webm?t=1769932821\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219410/extras/00f43c1494f13571f404844137e5d17a.mp4?t=1769932821\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Trolley Solution</strong> es una recopilación de minijuegos basada en el famoso dilema del tranvía, originalmente propuesto en 1967 por la filósofa británica Philippa Foot.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219410/extras/b1097ba16ab9c7cd45e8b344cd94187b.poster.avif?t=1769932821\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219410/extras/b1097ba16ab9c7cd45e8b344cd94187b.webm?t=1769932821\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219410/extras/b1097ba16ab9c7cd45e8b344cd94187b.mp4?t=1769932821\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Pon a prueba tu capacidad de pensamiento y elige entre la deontología y el utilitarismo en iteraciones humorísticas del problema. Desbloquea una variedad de minijuegos donde podrás poner a prueba tus habilidades de juego.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219410/extras/d8ccfb3daa059203ae9407fb68301719.poster.avif?t=1769932821\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219410/extras/d8ccfb3daa059203ae9407fb68301719.webm?t=1769932821\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219410/extras/d8ccfb3daa059203ae9407fb68301719.mp4?t=1769932821\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Desafíate a ti mismo y aprende conocimientos filosóficos importantes y útiles mientras expandes tu mente.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Características:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 20 variaciones del dilema del tranvía (más la original)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 20 minijuegos inspirados en cada variación</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Descargo de responsabilidad: Es posible que no aprendas nada útil o importante, ni expandas tu mente, al jugar este juego.</i></p>",
